OL,5, A couple have received an apology and a
OL,6, "very significant" financial payout    
OL,7, from a council over a failed adoption. 
OL,9,FSonny and Sarita Simak spent three     
OL,10,Fyears fighting to be reunited with a   
OL,11,Fboy they planned to adopt after he was 
OL,12,Fwrongly removed by Bradford Council.   
OL,14,FThey were approved by an independent   
OL,15,Fexpert and two adoption panels - but   
OL,16,Fthe council then told them he wasn't   
OL,17,Fsuitable for adoption.                 
OL,19,FThe council said it put the "interests 
OL,20,Fand wellbeing" of children at its core.
